divs: Sighting Detailsmy son and i decided to have a cigaret break around 330 am and as we were standing out side i looked up and saw a bright light just over the tree tops at first it did not appear to be moving but as we watched it became apperant it was rising higher as well as comming in our direction no blinkingg lights no pulsing just looked like a planet or large star till we realized it was moving then in the opposit direction another light appeared with blinking lights like a plane but unmoving we took four pictures on the cell phone but they are too grainy to see detail and get a perspective of size but the object was about four times the size of the surounding stars that were barely visible due to fog. earlier that day around 830 pm i saw two other shining objects while standing outside of work having a cigaret breakin that incident it first seemed to be one object which in a matter of seconds became two identical objects near each other. i am always watching the sky so it was not unusual for me to have looked up but this morning there was no missing it the light was very bright and the first thing i did was say to my son look a ufo at first he said it was probably a planet as it was too big to be a star but when we became certain it moved he told me to go in and get the phone to take the picture i was hesitant to leave him out there alone i did not loose sight of it in fact i am going back out to see if it is still there right now perhaps get a better picture i just wanted to know if any one else saw this light in waukesha wisconsin this morning
